MShLY ShLMH BN ChKM YShMCh-'aB VBN KSYL ThVGTh 'aMV.
L'a-YV'yYLV 'aVTShUrVTh UrSh'y VTShDQH ThTShYL MMVTh.
L'a-YUr'yYB YHVH NPhSh TShDYQ VHVTh UrSh'yYM YHDPh.
Ur'aSh 'yShH KPh-UrMYH VYD ChUrVTShYM Th'yShYUr.
'aGUr BQYTSh BN MShKYL NUrDM BQTShYUr BN MBYSh.
BUrKVTh LUr'aSh TShDYQ VPhY UrSh'yYM YKSH ChMS.
ZKUr TShDYQ LBUrKH VShM UrSh'yYM YUrQB.
ChKM-LB YQCh MTShVTh V'aVYL ShPhThYM YLBT.
HVLK BThM YLK BTCh VM'yQSh DUrKYV YVD'y.
QUrTSh 'yYN YThN 'yTShBTh V'aVYL ShPhThYM YLBT.
MQVUr ChYYM PhY TShDYQ VPhY UrSh'yYM YKSH ChMS.
ShN'aH Th'yVUrUr MDNYM V'yL KL-PhSh'yYM ThKSH 'aHBH.
BShPhThY NBVN ThMTSh'a ChKMH VShBT LGV ChSUr-LB.
ChKMYM YTShPhNV-D'yTh VPhY-'aVYL MChThH QUrBH.
HVN 'yShYUr QUrYTh 'yZV MChThTh DLYM UrYShM.
Ph'yLTh TShDYQ LChYYM ThBV'aTh UrSh'y LChT'aTh.
'aUrCh LChYYM ShVMUr MVSUr V'yVZB ThVKChTh MTh'yH.
MKSH ShN'aH ShPhThY-ShQUr VMVTSh'a DBH HV'a KSYL.
BUrB DBUrYM L'a YChDL-PhSh'y VChShK ShPhThYV MShKYL.
KSPh NBChUr LShVN TShDYQ LB UrSh'yYM KM'yT.
ShPhThY TShDYQ YUr'yV UrBYM V'aVYLYM BChSUr-LB YMVThV.
BUrKTh YHVH HY'a Th'yShYUr VL'a-YVSPh 'yTShB 'yMH.
KShChVQ LKSYL 'yShVTh ZMH VChKMH L'aYSh ThBVNH.
MGVUrTh UrSh'y HY'a ThBV'aNV VTh'aVTh TShDYQYM YThN.
K'yBVUr SVPhH V'aYN UrSh'y VTShDYQ YSVD 'yVLM.
KChMTSh LShNYM VK'yShN L'yYNYM KN H'yTShL LShLChYV.
